==English==

===Noun===
'''sonorant''' (''plural:'' '''[[sonorants]]''')

#(''phonetics'') a [[speech sound]] that is produced without turbulent airflow in the [[vocal tract]]; the generic term of [[vowel]], [[approximant]], [[nasal consonant]], etc.

